period we instruct. The third parties we may share personal information with are as follows:</p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1">Advertising, Direct Marketing, and Lead Generation</li>
</ul>
<p>ExoClick</p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1">Allow Users to Connect to Their Third-Party Accounts</li>
</ul>
<p>Twitter account, Pixiv account, Patreon account, DeviantArt account, Discord account and Github
account</p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1">User Account Registration and Authentication</li>
</ul>
<p>GitHub OAuth and Discord OAuth</p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1">Web and Mobile Analytics</li>
</ul>
<p>Microsoft Clarity</p>
<p>We also may need to share your personal information in the following situations:</p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1">Business Transfers. We may share or transfer your information in connection with,
or during negotiations of, any merger, sale of company assets, financing, or acquisition of all
