</ul>
<ol start="5">
<li>WHAT IS OUR STANCE ON THIRD-PARTY WEBSITES?</li>
</ol>
<p><em>In Short: We are not responsible for the safety of any information that you share with third
parties that we may link to or who advertise on our Services, but are not affiliated with, our
Services.</em></p>
<p>The Services may link to third-party websites, online services, or mobile applications and/or contain
